query:
INSERT INTO invoices (
    sender_id,
    recipient_id,
    invoice_number,
    quote_id,
    payment_due_date,
    payment_date,
    contract_id,
    project_id,
    remarks,
    total_before_vat,
    discount,
    vat_percentage,
    currency,
    total_after_vat,
    invoice_url,
    payment_request_url
) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
